metadata.name: The Tree of Secrets
metadata.description:
Secrets are hidden at the top of a tree in the middle of the forest that few know about. 
A witch and her giant cat are the only ones who know how to get to their tree-top house. By taking a potion that makes them tiny, they can go unnoticed in our world. 
The cat prepares potions in the cauldron while the witch practices her spells and summons spirits from other worlds. But one day, a curious spirit refuses to return to its world, defying the rules of the magical world.
